'''''Intractable''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] warship of unknown class that was present at the [[Battle of ThonBoka]]. Its captain questioned [[Rokur Gepta]]'s tactics before the main battle. The [[Sorcerers of Tund/Legends|Sorcerer of Tund]] subsequently ordered both the captain and his second in command thrown out an airlock for being individualist.

